{"tid":1466874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位今日機場既手足入黎，捉鬼改善地方","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:10.000Z","uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"207a9986259cad81539c03d0d93d8a5c8918c5c3","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日大家捉到都好叻，但之後處理手法可以改善一下<br />\n第一，捉到之後綁起佢冇問題，但又唔使全部人都推曬上去，只係要十個手足就應該可以綁到，太多人只會太亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，影相當然要啦，但盡量唔好打佢，我明大家想還眼，但羞辱佢效果更好，打佢只是身理上，但羞辱係心理上，可以令佢地心理上怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，今日有阻first aid 阻救護阻消防，呢樣下次一定唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為佢地職責係救人，無論係邊一面都會救，所以唔可以阻佢地，戰場上敵人受有first aid 救走都唔會有人阻，我地都唔應該阻，唔可以學黑警咁阻first aid 救人</span>"},{"pid":"312e51fa461c5f6f1be1d779b4e2089da2204ca2","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日大家都做得好好已經，下次再做好啲</span></strong></span><br />\n不分化 不割蓆 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"40c19104ecc2157440590588abaea5af434d5245","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"612 721 85 811"},{"pid":"0082a6d9aef389be04894addaff489b1cb8c42f7","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋下次影完佢相就送埋一邊唔好理佢啦</span>"},{"pid":"9f742e05373bcf3e7d15cc00270ac1a1a7f42ec0","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b55e7377d510b856896a889720f271f614e50e","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c233b7cde3880589f2b41cbb6d67560d350c51d0","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白"},{"pid":"1433e9a5760ff93778076e812809eb186e434593","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a9ca9c6b97f4f3fbe6d34d401b40ad9062e74e","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e19cfd9532ce1aa9cc6e5b92ad55ab9fcb63a3","tid":1466874,"uid":206546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}